title: BRIEF-Erste Group Bank in merchant payments services jv
text:
July 27 Erste Group Bank Ag
* Erste group and Global Payments together with Caixabank form joint venture in cee to provide merchant payments services
* Transaction is expected to close during q4 2015 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Frankfurt Newsroom)
